  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/746d01306078ed732c9eb2c25dbb4d49.poster.avif?t=1695952876\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/746d01306078ed732c9eb2c25dbb4d49.webm?t=1695952876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/746d01306078ed732c9eb2c25dbb4d49.mp4?t=1695952876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/4329d922b79e2bada3988367db3aca2b.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>In an unfamiliar location with unfamiliar people. You are Elina and you're... That's a good question, who are you? Were you drugged? It's up to you to figure out how you got here and why, and the massive implications for the future... and the past.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/a668edb5471ca9a99d1a20bbf8067c77.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>How you treat your fellow captives will affect your ending. Will you trust them... or will you throw them to the wolves?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/5314fca4a22799f72eee486a83d60de4.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>You will be subject to a variety of puzzles, (mostly ciphers)(Most are skippable), to discover more about the facility, your companions... and yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/f51c61d88eac251fb16861ace82002ac.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>The story contains (At least) 8 endings, including a true ending that requires information gathered from other paths to access.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/11ee30028663e50e4acc85fd355b8e9a.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>Featuring a flow chart that unlocks as you progress, allowing you to jump back and forth to try different decisions.<br><br>Will you uncover the mystery? Can you preserve your life... and your consciousness until the very end?<br><br>4-6 hours playtime.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/746d01306078ed732c9eb2c25dbb4d49.poster.avif?t=1695952876\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/746d01306078ed732c9eb2c25dbb4d49.webm?t=1695952876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/746d01306078ed732c9eb2c25dbb4d49.mp4?t=1695952876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/4329d922b79e2bada3988367db3aca2b.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>In an unfamiliar location with unfamiliar people. You are Elina and you're... That's a good question, who are you? Were you drugged? It's up to you to figure out how you got here and why, and the massive implications for the future... and the past.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/a668edb5471ca9a99d1a20bbf8067c77.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>How you treat your fellow captives will affect your ending. Will you trust them... or will you throw them to the wolves?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/5314fca4a22799f72eee486a83d60de4.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>You will be subject to a variety of puzzles, (mostly ciphers)(Most are skippable), to discover more about the facility, your companions... and yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/f51c61d88eac251fb16861ace82002ac.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>The story contains (At least) 8 endings, including a true ending that requires information gathered from other paths to access.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066380/extras/11ee30028663e50e4acc85fd355b8e9a.webp?t=1695952876\" width=610 height=36 /></span><br>Featuring a flow chart that unlocks as you progress, allowing you to jump back and forth to try different decisions.<br><br>Will you uncover the mystery? Can you preserve your life... and your consciousness until the very end?<br><br>4-6 hours playtime.",
